---
title: Bombay Veggie Mince & Coconut Curry with Garlic Rice & Roasted Cashews
description: If you're looking for an extra delicious veggie alternative for an Indian-syle curry, you've come to the right place. Introducing
(drum roll please) our new veggie mince! It's the perfect substitute for a meat-free Monday, and still packed with all the same
flavours and textures that you love in a creamy curry and rice dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bombay-veggie-mince-coconut-curry-ab642564.jpg
